Application.Domain

Class Feelings

  • java.lang.Object
    • Application.Domain.Feelings

  • @Entity
public class Feelings
extends java.lang.Object
    Feelings is the class that maps the database Entity Feelings. The Feelings represent the sentiment expressed by the User.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Corti Lorenzo, Tocchetti Andrea
